"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-news-uk-prime-minister-olympians-government-downing-street-paris-b2614449.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Sir Keir Starmer said he wants to see greater access to sport for all children, as he metOlympiansand Paralympians in Downing Street's garden.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keir_Starmer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sir Keir Starmer\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keir_Starmer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keir_Starmer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a speech at Number 10, thePrime Ministersaid access to sports facilities is \\\"vital\\\" to children's development and to local communities.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, Sir Keir thanked Team GB's medal-adorned athletes for giving the UK \\\"one of the greatest summers of Olympic and Paralympic sport\\\", adding that he was \\\"glued to the television\\\".\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 666, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999794827873995, \"rank\": 1.492530753024688e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9924661256154443, \"rank\": 0.007590074305978766, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 754, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9993149882896974, \"rank\": 0.0006854812729224014, \"text\": \"Paralympic sport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on to say: \\\"You have demonstrated the power, not only of the human spirit to triumph against the odds, but of sport to bring people together and to break down barriers, and promote fitness and health.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And that's something I want to see much more of under thisGovernment, because I know how important sport is to local communities (and) for children's development, and how vital it is that they have access to sports facilities.\\\"\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just think about all the people - particularly young people - who will have watched you, and because they have watched you, have got that spark to think, I could be the next you,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sir Keir specifically congratulated Paralympic medalist Poppy Maskill, who won three golds and two silvers at the games inParis, adding: \\\"Absolutely amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1610, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poppy\", \"score\": 0.9473497433047837, \"rank\": 0.03285477170849575, \"text\": \"Poppy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poppy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poppy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swimmer Ms Maskill told the PA news agency it was \\\"pretty cool\\\" to be invited toDowning Street, as it was something she \\\"never\\\" thought she would be asked to do.\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1773, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1911, \"entities\": []}]}"